(yue) 噉講又係𠸏
(en) It's not like that


21
00:02:44,453 --> 00:02:47,440
(yue) 芙莉蓮，你跟住落嚟嘅人生
(en) Frieren, your future life


22
00:02:47,772 --> 00:02:50,049
(yue) 一定會比我哋可以想象得到嘅
(en) Will certainly be more than we can imagine


23
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,850
(yue)更加漫長得多啊嗬？
(en) Much longer, right?


24
00:02:52,438 --> 00:02:53,760
(yue) 我諗應該係喇
(en) I think so


25
00:03:02,438 --> 00:03:07,971
(yue) 《葬送的芙莉蓮》
