26
00:03:30,914 --> 00:03:33,004
(yue) 勇者欣梅爾
(en) Brave warrior, Xinmei


27
00:03:33,029 --> 00:03:34,554
(yue) 戰士艾冉
(en) Warrior, Airen


28
00:03:34,825 --> 00:03:36,007
(yue) 僧侶海塔
(en) Monk, Haita


29
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,867
(yue) 魔法使芙莉蓮
(en) Sorceress, Frieren


30
00:03:39,416 --> 00:03:43,154
(yue) 你哋今次成功打敗咗魔王做得好好
(en) You have done well in defeating the demon king this time


31
00:03:43,514 --> 00:03:47,281
(yue) 從此，世界將會迎嚟和平嘅時代
(en) From now on, the world will enter a peaceful era


32
