(yue) 會整我哋嘅雕像放喺廣場嗰度啊
(en) will build our statues in the square


34
00:04:12,652 --> 00:04:14,358
(yue) 不過，個雕像究竟可唔可以真實還原到
(en) But can the statue truly restore


35
00:04:14,358 --> 00:04:17,078
(yue) 我呢個咁俊俏不凡嘅樣呢？
(en) my handsome appearance?


36
00:04:17,129 --> 00:04:20,445
(yue) 講真我好有保留囖
(en) Honestly, I have some reservations


37
