(yue) 佢哋班人真係現實
(en) They are really realistic


38
00:04:22,332 --> 00:04:24,232
(yue) 好喇，算數啦，芙莉蓮
(en) Alright, don't worry, Frieren


39
00:04:24,283 --> 00:04:26,951
(yue) 橫掂而家可以噉樣免費任飲酒
(en) Now we can drink for free


40
00:04:27,128 --> 00:04:28,955
(yue) 噉樣已經夠啦，係咪啊？
(en) That's enough, right?


41
00:04:29,434 --> 00:04:30,824
(yue) 你個酒肉和尚
(en) You, the wine and meat monk


42
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,555
(yue) 旅程已經完結喇
(en) The journey has ended


43
00:04:41,344 --> 00:04:42,209
(yue) 講得啱啊
(en) That's right


44
00:04:43,455 --> 00:04:45,577
(yue) 我哋嘅冒險到呢度終於都完喇
(en) Our adventure has finally ended here


45
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:48,270
(yue) 已經十年喇
(en) It's been ten years


46
00:04:49,078 --> 00:04:51,324
(yue) 喺呢段時間發生咗好多事
(en) Many things have happened during this time


47
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:54,148
(yue) 我記得出發嗰一日
(en) I remember the day we set out


48
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:57,057
(yue) 欣梅爾同艾冉對國王陛下不敬
(en) Xinmei and Airen were disrespectful to His Majesty the King


49
00:04:57,067 --> 00:04:58,388
(yue) 爭啲被處死
(en) They were almost put to death


50
00:04:58,745 --> 00:05:01,648
(yue) 一唔小心我哋嘅冒險可能會喺嗰度完
(en) Our adventure might have ended there if we weren't careful


51
00:05:03,031 --> 00:05:04,989
(yue) 海塔仲試過因為宿醉一啲用都冇
(en) Haita even tried to use his skills while hungover


52
00:05:05,047 --> 00:05:06,522
(yue) 連路都行唔到啊
(en) He couldn't even walk


53
00:05:11,266 --> 00:05:14,506
(yue) 你塊面青到好似不死族噉喎，冇嘢吖嘛？
(en) Your face is as pale as an undead, are you okay?


54
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:17,180
(yue) -唔得喇
-都估到你㗎喇
(en) -It can't be helped
-It was expected of you


55
00:05:17,231 --> 00:05:19,784
(yue) 佢每個禮拜都會有一次醉到噉
(en) He gets drunk like this every week


56
00:05:19,835 --> 00:05:21,769
(yue) 喺呢方面嘅話，我就好優秀
(en) In this aspect, I'm excellent


57
00:05:21,794 --> 00:05:24,032
(yue) -你爭啲畀寶箱怪食咗嗰陣
-好黑啊，好得人驚啊
(en) -When you were eaten by the treasure chest monster
-It was so dark, so scary


58
00:05:24,056 --> 00:05:25,434
(yue) 我哋有諗過抌低你㗎
(en) We thought of abandoning you


59
00:05:25,494 --> 00:05:28,516
(yue) -同你講咗好多次係陷阱啦，仲中招
-你哋唔好企喺度快啲過嚟幫下我啦，好驚
(en) -We told you many times it was a trap, but you still fell for it
-Don't just stand there, hurry up and help me, it's scary


60
00:05:28,567 --> 00:05:30,114
(yue) -蠢成咁不如抌低佢喇
-唔好，唔好食我啊
(en) -It's better to abandon him
-No, don't eat me


61
00:05:35,259 --> 00:05:36,340
(yue) 真係吖
(en) Really


62
00:05:36,847 --> 00:05:38,729
(yue) 淨係諗到啲搞笑嘅回憶啊
(en) I only think of funny memories


63
00:05:40,058 --> 00:05:41,363
(yue) 不過真係好開心啊
(en) But it's really happy


64
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:45,220
(yue) 我好慶幸可以同你哋一齊冒險係真㗎
(en) I'm really glad I could adventure with you guys


65
00:05:46,125 --> 00:05:47,587
(yue) 冇錯，講得啱啊
(en) That's right, you're right


66
00:05:47,863 --> 00:05:49,999
(yue) 雖然呢段冒險嘅時間有啲短
(en) Although this adventure was a bit short


67
00:05:50,610 --> 00:05:53,220
(yue) 你話有啲短？你喺度講咩啊？
(en) You say it's short? What are you talking about?


68
00:05:53,244 --> 00:05:54,676
(yue) 成十年喎
(en) It's been ten years


69
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:58,220
(yue) 你睇下海塔，已經由後生仔變咗做大叔喇
(en) Look at Haita, he's already become an old man from a young guy


70
00:05:58,271 --> 00:05:59,517
(yue) 你噉講嘢㗎？
(en) Are you kidding?


71
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:01,449
(yue) 佢本來就係大叔
(en) He was an old man from the start


72
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,993
(yue) 連你都噉講？
(en) Are you also like that?


73
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:11,245
(yue) 差唔多要開始喇
(en) It's about to start


74
00:06:19,767 --> 00:06:22,080
(yue) 好似係叫半世紀流星，係咪啊？
(en) It's called the Half-Century Meteor, right?


75
00:06:22,876 --> 00:06:25,730
(yue) 50年先會出現一次嘅流星雨
(en) A meteor shower that only appears once every 50 years


76
00:06:26,973 --> 00:06:29,973
(yue) 好啱用嚟做揭開呢個和平時代嘅序幕啊
(en) It's perfect for opening the curtain of this peaceful era


77
00:06:32,793 --> 00:06:33,893
(yue) 真係好靚啊
(en) It's really beautiful


78
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,921
(yue) 喺呢個城鎮好難睇得清啊
(en) It's hard to see clearly in this town


79
00:06:36,972 --> 00:06:38,773
(yue) 我而家喺度感動緊㗎
(en) I'm being moved to tears now


80
00:06:38,852 --> 00:06:40,244
(yue) 唔好破壞個氣氛啦
(en) Don't ruin the atmosphere


81
00:06:42,324 --> 00:06:43,270
(yue) 係噉，下次
(en) Okay, next time


82
00:06:45,401 --> 00:06:48,870
(yue) 50年之後，我知有個睇得更加清楚嘅地方
(en) 50 years later, I know a place where we can see it more clearly


83
00:06:48,921 --> 00:06:49,934
(yue) 我帶你哋去吖
(en) I'll take you there


84
00:06:53,542 --> 00:06:54,434
(yue) 笑咩啊？
(en) Are you laughing?


85
00:06:54,666 --> 00:06:55,398
(yue) 冇
(en) No


86
00:06:55,956 --> 00:06:56,979
(yue) 咩事都冇啊
(en) Nothing's wrong


87
00:06:58,829 --> 00:06:59,820
(yue) 就噉話啦
(en) Just saying


88
00:07:00,671 --> 00:07:02,069
(yue) 大家一齊去睇
(en) Let's go see together


89
00:07:24,707 --> 00:07:26,354
(yue) 係噉，喺度講再見喇
(en) Okay, let's say goodbye for now


90
00:07:26,992 --> 00:07:28,680
(yue) 跟住你有咩打算啊？
(en) What are your plans from now on?


91
00:07:29,219 --> 00:07:31,150
(yue) 我諗住繼續收集魔法
(en) I plan to continue collecting magic


92
00:07:31,617 --> 00:07:35,189
(yue) 我預計會用一百年左右行勻成個中央諸國
(en) I estimate it will take around 100 years to travel around the central nations


93
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,253
(yue) 不過，我間中會揾下你哋𠸏
(en) However, I'll occasionally look for you guys


94
00:07:42,529 --> 00:07:45,197
(yue) 精靈嘅時間觀念真係好難理解
(en) Elves have a hard-to-understand concept of time


95
00:07:45,221 --> 00:07:47,840
(yue) 咪係囖，佢究竟可以生存幾耐呢？
(en) Right, how long can they survive?


96
00:07:48,488 --> 00:07:51,417
(yue) 無論係50年定100年，對佢嚟講
(en) Whether it's 50 years or 100 years, for them


97
00:07:51,528 --> 00:07:53,700
(yue) 或者都只係一啲微不足道嘅時間
(en) it's just a insignificant amount of time


98
00:08:44,295 --> 00:08:46,424
(yue) 你話暗黑龍嘅角？
(en) You mean the dark dragon's horn?


99
00:08:46,502 --> 00:08:49,208
(yue) 我哋鋪頭冇賣呢樣嘢啝
(en) Our shop doesn't sell that kind of thing


100
00:08:49,348 --> 00:08:53,283
(yue)就算係暗黑龍都已經二三十年冇見過喇
(en) The dark dragon hasn't been seen for 20 or 30 years


101
00:08:53,307 --> 00:08:55,395
(yue) 係呀？噉就麻煩喇
(en) Really? Then it's troublesome


102
00:08:55,485 --> 00:08:57,108
(yue) 召喚嗰陣要用㗎
(en) It's needed for summoning


103
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:02,478
(yue) 係喎，之前係魔王城執到嘅角
(en) Yes, it's the horn we obtained from the demon king's castle


104
00:09:03,126 --> 00:09:05,045
(yue) 應該仲放喺欣梅爾嗰度
(en) It should still be with Xinmei


105
00:09:05,970 --> 00:09:09,350
(yue) 硬係覺得佢散發住好邪惡嘅氣息啊
(en) I still feel it emits a very evil aura


106
00:09:09,403 --> 00:09:11,220
(yue) 但係應該對人冇害㗎嗬？
(en) But it shouldn't harm humans, right?


107
00:09:11,244 --> 00:09:12,343
(yue) 我唔知啊
(en) I don't know


108
00:09:12,394 --> 00:09:13,947
(yue) 連你都唔知呀？
(en) You don't know either?


109
00:09:14,912 --> 00:09:17,456
(yue) 就嚟又到半世紀流星嘅時候
(en) It's almost time for the Half-Century Meteor again


110
00:09:17,507 --> 00:09:18,963
(yue) 順便睇下佢點樣啦
(en) Let's take a look at it then


111
00:09:25,185 --> 00:09:28,501
(yue) 同上次嚟嗰陣比條街真係唔同咗好多
(en) The street is really different from last time


112
00:09:43,165 --> 00:09:44,907
(yue) 我記得喺呢度附近㗎喎
(en) I remember it's around here


113
00:09:45,585 --> 00:09:46,794
(yue) 芙莉蓮？
(en) Frieren?


114
00:09:47,865 --> 00:09:48,834
(yue) 欣梅爾？
(en) Xinmei?


115
00:09:55,893 --> 00:09:57,155
(yue) 你老咗好多啊
(en) You've aged a lot


116
00:09:57,212 --> 00:09:59,167
(yue) 講嘢咁過分㗎
(en) That's a bit too much to say


117
00:10:01,068 --> 00:10:04,560
(yue)就算我而家老咗，都仲幾俊俏吖
(en) Even though I'm old now, I'm still quite handsome


118
00:10:06,395 --> 00:10:08,575
(yue) 已經50年冇見喇
(en) It's been 50 years since we last met


119
00:10:08,622 --> 00:10:11,404
(yue) 你個樣仲係同以前一模一樣
(en) You still look the same as before


120
00:10:12,113 --> 00:10:15,396
(yue) 我仲以為呢一世都唔會再見到你喇
(en) I thought I wouldn't see you again in this life


121
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:19,917
(yue) 半世紀流星呀？
(en) The Half-Century Meteor?


122
00:10:19,968 --> 00:10:21,484
(yue) 好令人懷念啊
(en) It's so nostalgic


123
00:10:21,846 --> 00:10:24,876
(yue) 仲有就係關於係魔王城執到嘅嗰樣嘢
(en) And also, about the thing we obtained from the demon king's castle


124
00:10:24,927 --> 00:10:27,386
(yue) 你係咪講咁黑龍嘅角啊？
(en) Are you talking about the dark dragon's horn?


125
00:10:27,410 --> 00:10:30,589
(yue) 關於呢樣嘢，我從來都冇忘記過
(en) I've never forgotten about that thing


126
00:10:30,613 --> 00:10:34,190
(yue) 因為佢一直喺個櫃裏面散發邪惡嘅氣息
(en) Because it's always emitting an evil aura from the cabinet


127
00:10:34,826 --> 00:10:36,123
(yue) 真係唔好意思
(en) I'm really sorry


128
00:10:36,737 --> 00:10:40,175
(yue) 其實你求其揾個倉庫
(en) Actually, if you just find a warehouse


129
00:10:40,175 --> 00:10:43,730
(yue) 放佢入去唔理佢咪得囖
(en) and put it there, it's fine


130
00:10:42,163 --> 00:10:43,730
(yue) 噉樣點得嗄？
(en) How is that?


131
00:10:47,344 --> 00:10:52,043
(yue) 對你嚟講，或者佢可能
(en) For you, it might be


132
00:10:52,094 --> 00:10:53,581
(yue) 只係一樣隨便寄放喺我度嘅嘢
(en) just something casually left with me


133
00:10:53,631 --> 00:10:57,602
(yue) 但係對我嚟講
(en) But for me


134
00:10:57,659 --> 00:11:01,763
(yue) 佢係重要嘅同伴託付畀我嘅貴重物品嚟𠺢
(en) it's a precious item entrusted to me by an important companion


135
00:11:10,142 --> 00:11:12,777
(yue) 明明呢樣嘢根本就一啲都唔重要
(en) Clearly, this thing is not important at all


136
00:11:32,607 --> 00:11:33,934
(yue) 欣梅爾仲未得嗱？
(en) Has Xinmei not arrived yet?


137
00:11:34,843 --> 00:11:37,522
(yue) 你冇頭髮花時間打扮都冇意思啦
(en) You don't even take the time to dress up


138
00:11:38,429 --> 00:11:40,896
(yue) 光頭都有光頭嘅堅持㗎
(en) Being bald has its own persistence


139
00:11:48,232 --> 00:11:49,125
(yue) 好喇
(en) Okay


140
00:11:49,176 --> 00:11:51,925
(yue) 我哋而家去睇半世紀流星喇
(en) Let's go see the Half-Century Meteor now


141
00:12:00,185 --> 00:12:02,555
(yue) 你變到好有威嚴喎，海塔
(en) You've become very majestic, Haita


142
00:12:02,895 --> 00:12:05,071
(yue) 因為我係聖都嘅主教啊
(en) Because I'm the bishop of the holy city


143
00:12:05,095 --> 00:12:07,588
(yue) 芙莉蓮，你真係一啲都冇變啊
(en) Frieren, you really haven't changed at all


144
00:12:08,311 --> 00:12:09,835
(yue) 唔好摸我個頭啦
(en) Don't touch my head


145
00:12:11,561 --> 00:12:13,850
(yue) 艾冉你個樣冇乜點變過啊
(en) Airen, you haven't changed much either


146
00:12:14,508 --> 00:12:16,681
(yue) 係咩？睇落冇變呀？
(en) What? You look the same?


147
00:12:16,941 --> 00:12:18,656
(yue) 不愧係矮人族啊
(en) As expected of the dwarves


148
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:21,726
(yue) 係噉，你話睇得更加清楚嘅地方喺邊啊？
(en) So, where is the place where we can see it more clearly?


149
00:12:21,777 --> 00:12:22,708
(yue) 嗯？
(en) Hm?


150
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:24,375
(yue) 而家就出發去呀？
(en) Are we leaving now?


151
00:12:24,567 --> 00:12:26,788
(yue) 距離出現半世紀流星嘅時期
(en) Until the time of the Half-Century Meteor


152
00:12:26,839 --> 00:12:28,528
(yue) 應該仲有段時間喎
(en) there should still be some time


153
00:12:28,660 --> 00:12:29,428
(yue) 嗯
(en) Yeah


154
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:32,564
(yue) 因為要由呢度行一個禮拜過去㗎
(en) Because we have to walk for a week to get there


155
00:12:33,041 --> 00:12:34,863
(yue) 咩話？要行咁遠？
(en) What? Do we have to walk that far?


156
00:12:35,303 --> 00:12:39,049
(yue) 真係吖，噉折磨老人家㗎
(en) Really, it's like torturing an old man


157
00:12:42,523 --> 00:12:44,143
(yue) 好懷念啊
(en) It's so nostalgic


158
00:12:44,455 --> 00:12:48,029
(yue) 而家噉樣行，就好似返返去嗰陣噉
(en) Walking like this now, it's just like when we used to


159
00:12:52,619 --> 00:12:55,530
(yue) 我哋去咗好多唔同嘅地方旅行
(en) We've traveled to many different places


160
00:12:56,244 --> 00:12:58,590
(yue) 所有嘢都覺得好新鮮
(en) Everything felt new


161
00:12:59,345 --> 00:13:01,556
(yue) 而且睇落好耀眼
(en) And it was dazzling


162
00:13:26,094 --> 00:13:29,001
(yue) 喺我咁多美麗嘅回憶入面
(en) Among my many beautiful memories


163
00:13:29,052 --> 00:13:31,421
(yue) 一直都有你哋陪住我
(en) You guys have always been with me


164
00:13:34,346 --> 00:13:35,454
(yue) 我一直
(en) I have always


165
00:13:36,073 --> 00:13:40,390
(yue) 都好期待我哋所有人可以再次聚埋一齊㗎
(en) looked forward to us all being together again


166
00:13:40,414 --> 00:13:42,708
(yue) 好多謝你啊，芙莉蓮
(en) Thank you, Frieren


167
00:13:43,487 --> 00:13:45,390
(yue) 都係多得你
(en) It's all thanks to you


168
00:13:45,414 --> 00:13:49,150
(yue) 我先可以體驗到最後一次開心嘅冒險
(en) I was able to experience one last happy adventure


169
00:14:12,766 --> 00:14:14,504
(yue) 好靚啊
(en) It's beautiful


170
00:14:41,679 --> 00:14:45,080
(yue) 欣梅爾佢，就嗰陣一定覺得好幸福㗎喇
(en) Xinmei must have been very happy then


171
00:14:46,783 --> 00:14:47,892
(yue) 真係噉咩？
(en) Really?


172
00:14:55,103 --> 00:14:58,360
(yue) 聽講嗰個女仔係欣梅爾大人嘅同伴嚟啊
(en) I heard that girl was Xinmei's companion


173
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,829
(yue) 但係睇落一啲都唔傷心𠸏
(en) But she doesn't look sad at all


174
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,494
(yue) 真係好無情啊
(en) It's really heartless


175
00:15:03,969 --> 00:15:05,041
(yue) 哎吔…
(en) Ah…


176
00:15:05,065 --> 00:15:07,354
(yue) 我哋兩個睇落都唔傷心喎
(en) We two don't look sad either


177
00:15:07,405 --> 00:15:09,155
(yue) 主教，你莊重啲啦
(en) Bishop, be more solemn


178
00:15:09,179 --> 00:15:10,530
(yue) 你真係冇人性啊！
(en) You really have no humanity!


179
00:15:11,425 --> 00:15:13,071
(yue) 畀人秒殺啊
(en) You're being killed instantly


180
00:15:37,366 --> 00:15:38,619
(yue) 因為我根本…
(en) Because I fundamentally...


181
00:15:39,112 --> 00:15:41,119
(yue) 一啲都唔了解欣梅爾佢
(en) don't understand Xinmei at all


182
00:15:53,934 --> 00:15:55,452
(yue) 我哋只不過係…
(en) We were just...


183
00:15:55,705 --> 00:15:57,413
(yue) 一齊旅行咗十年吒嘛
(en) traveling together for ten years


184
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:06,881
(yue) 我明明知道人類嘅壽命
(en) I clearly know that human lifespan


185
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:08,920
(yue) 不嬲都好短
(en) is very short


186
00:16:10,367 --> 00:16:11,650
(yue) 點解冇諗過…
(en) Why didn't I think about...


187
00:16:12,773 --> 00:16:14,654
(yue) 多啲去了解下佢呢？
(en) getting to know him better?


188
00:16:24,318 --> 00:16:26,400
(yue) 唔好摸我個頭啦
(en) Don't touch my head


189
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:37,890
(yue) 我都係時候要返去聖都㗎喇
(en) It's time for me to return to the holy city


190
00:16:41,503 --> 00:16:44,060
(yue) 等我再好好睇下你哋個樣啦
(en) Let me take a good look at your faces again


191
00:16:44,702 --> 00:16:46,673
(yue) 今次係我哋最後一次見面喇
(en) This is our last meeting


192
00:16:47,296 --> 00:16:48,693
(yue) 你係咪唔舒服啊？
(en) Are you not feeling well?


193
00:16:48,886 --> 00:16:51,569
(yue) 飲酒飲得太痛搞到周身病痛
(en) Drinking too much has made my whole body ache


194
00:16:51,593 --> 00:16:53,108
(yue) 而家報應到哩？
(en) Is this karma?


195
00:16:54,541 --> 00:16:57,793
(yue) 如果你哋有日去開聖都，記得帶支酒
(en) If you guys ever go to the holy city, remember to bring some wine


196
00:16:57,817 --> 00:16:59,121
(yue) 去我墳度拜我啊
(en) and visit my grave


197
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:03,723
(yue) 海塔你，真係一啲都唔驚死咩？
(en) Haita, you're not afraid of death at all?


198
00:17:05,957 --> 00:17:09,586
(yue) 我哋幾個係拯救世界嘅勇者隊成員嚟𠺢嘛
(en) We're members of the brave warrior team that saved the world


199
00:17:09,766 --> 00:17:13,080
(yue) 死咗之後，唔使問一定係上天堂享福
(en) After death, we'll definitely go to heaven and enjoy happiness


200
00:17:14,182 --> 00:17:15,643
(yue) 我都係為咗噉樣
(en) That's why


201
00:17:15,693 --> 00:17:17,799
(yue) 先會同你哋一齊去戰鬥㗎咋
(en) I'll go to battle with you guys


202
00:17:18,295 --> 00:17:19,799
(yue) 你個酒肉和尚
(en) You, the wine and meat monk


203
00:17:22,132 --> 00:17:23,568
(yue) 係噉，我走先喇
(en) Okay, I'll leave first


204
00:17:32,021 --> 00:17:34,680
(yue) 好啦，我都係時候要走喇
(en) Okay, it's time for me to leave too


205
00:17:35,662 --> 00:17:37,635
(yue) 繼續收集魔法之類？
(en) Continue collecting magic?


206
00:17:37,938 --> 00:17:40,028
(yue) 嗯，呢個都係目的之一
(en) Yes, that's one of my goals


207
00:17:40,822 --> 00:17:43,488
(yue) 但係我仲想去試下多啲了解人類
(en) But I also want to try to understand humans more


208
00:17:45,878 --> 00:17:46,733
(yue) 乜係？
(en) What's up?


209
00:17:47,982 --> 00:17:50,183
(yue) 我有一件事想同你商量啊
(en) I have something to discuss with you


210
00:17:50,343 --> 00:17:52,118
(yue) 因為我係用魔法𠺢嘛
(en) Because I use magic


211
00:17:52,169 --> 00:17:55,030
(yue) 所以如果身邊有個強大嘅先鋒就好喇
(en) so it would be good to have a strong vanguard by my side


212
00:17:55,081 --> 00:17:56,609
(yue) 你都係放過我啦
(en) You can spare me


213
00:17:57,301 --> 00:18:00,835
(yue) 我已經年紀大到揮唔郁把斧頭喇
(en) I'm too old to swing an axe


214
00:18:03,363 --> 00:18:05,698
(yue) 唔好噉嘅表情啦，芙莉蓮
(en) Don't make that face, Frieren


215
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:09,174
(yue) 人嘅一生喺歲老之後嘅時間
(en) A person's life after old age


216
00:18:09,224 --> 00:18:11,142
(yue) 比想象中要長嘅
(en) is longer than imagined


217
00:18:13,330 --> 00:18:13,916
(yue) 係呀？
(en) Really?


218
00:18:14,916 --> 00:18:16,643
(yue) 噉再見喇，艾冉
(en) See you later, Airen


219
00:18:17,429 --> 00:18:19,017
(yue) 啊，再見
(en) See you


220
00:18:53,485 --> 00:18:56,945
(yue) （第一話：冒險結束）
(en) (Episode 1: The Adventure Ends)


221
00:19:00,984 --> 00:19:02,718
(yue) 係頭先棵樹呀？
(en) Is that the tree from before?


222
00:19:02,769 --> 00:19:05,078
(yue) 每次嚟呢個森林都會蕩失路
(en) I get lost every time I come to this forest


223
00:19:05,196 --> 00:19:06,425
(yue) 呢度係邊度啊？
(en) Where is this place?


224
00:19:07,105 --> 00:19:10,310
(yue) （勇者欣梅爾死之後20年）
(en) (20 years after the death of brave warrior Xinmei)


225
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,020
(yue) 請問你係咪揾緊咩啊？
(en) Excuse me, are you looking for something?


226
00:19:18,697 --> 00:19:20,446
(yue) 請問係咪有咩事啊？
(en) Is something wrong?


227
00:19:21,352 --> 00:19:25,033
(yue) 噉𠸏，我喺度揾緊一個
(en) I'm looking for someone


228
00:19:25,084 --> 00:19:27,839
(yue) 叫海塔嘅人嘅屋企啊
(en) named Haita's house


229
00:19:30,819 --> 00:19:33,020
(yue) 原來你係海塔大人嘅客人呀？
(en) You're a guest of Haita's?


230
00:19:34,804 --> 00:19:36,561
(yue) 你個酒肉和尚仲好地地喎
(en) You're still a wine and meat monk


231
00:19:36,612 --> 00:19:38,637
(yue) 想好有型噉死
(en) Wanting to die in style


232
00:19:38,688 --> 00:19:41,050
(yue) 都唔係件容易嘅事嚟㗎
(en) It's not an easy thing to do


233
00:19:41,608 --> 00:19:42,810
(yue) 我仲買咗酒諗住放喺你個墳前面
(en) I bought wine to put in front of your grave


234
00:19:42,867 --> 00:19:44,770
(yue) 飲唔飲返杯啊？
(en) Want to have a drink?


235
00:19:45,129 --> 00:19:45,890
(yue) 係呀？
(en) Really?


236
00:19:46,736 --> 00:19:48,839
(yue) 而家先開始改過自新
(en) I've started to reform


237
00:19:48,890 --> 00:19:51,699
(yue) 我諗女神大人應該都唔會就噉原諒你
(en) I think the goddess won't forgive you that easily


238
00:19:58,953 --> 00:20:00,519
(yue) 真係唔該晒你啊
(en) Thank you


239
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:07,009
(yue) 佢係邊個啊？
(en) Who is he?


240
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:08,479
(yue) 佢個名叫做費倫
(en) His name is Ferren


241
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:12,209
(yue) 係南方諸國嘅戰爭留落嚟嘅孤兒
(en) He's an orphan from the war in the southern nations


242
00:20:13,553 --> 00:20:14,760
(yue) 好唔似你喎
(en) He's not like you


243
00:20:15,306 --> 00:20:18,353
(yue) 你不嬲都唔係嗰種會熱心助人嘅人嚟
(en) You're not the type to enthusiastically help others


244
00:20:18,748 --> 00:20:20,233
(yue) 同欣梅爾好唔同
(en) Unlike Xinmei


245
00:20:22,905 --> 00:20:25,479
(yue) 芙莉蓮，你嚟我呢度做咩啊？
(en) Frieren, why are you here?


246
00:20:26,293 --> 00:20:28,633
(yue) 我去聖都買嘢順便嚟睇你
(en) I came to the holy city to buy things and visit you


247
00:20:28,980 --> 00:20:32,280
(yue) 因為我而家會盡量
(en) Because I'll try my best


248
00:20:33,765 --> 00:20:36,467
(yue) 同旅途中遇到嘅人多啲互動
(en) to interact with the people I meet on my journey


249
00:20:36,605 --> 00:20:38,447
(yue) 再加上，我仲爭海塔你好多人情
(en) and I also owe you a lot, Haita


250
00:20:42,121 --> 00:20:44,137
(yue) 係噉有件事想拜託你
(en) So I have a favor to ask of you


251
00:20:44,195 --> 00:20:44,727
(yue) 嗯？
(en) Hm?


252
00:20:45,669 --> 00:20:47,330
(yue) 你有冇諗過收徒弟？
(en) Have you thought about taking an apprentice?


253
00:20:49,487 --> 00:20:52,597
(yue) 費倫佢，好有做一個魔法師嘅資質
(en) Ferren has a lot of potential to be a magician


254
00:20:53,224 --> 00:20:56,097
(yue) 你可唔可以帶埋佢同你一齊去旅行啊？
(en) Can you take him with you on your travels?


255
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:00,640
(yue) 對唔住啊，海塔
(en) Sorry, Haita


256
00:21:00,691 --> 00:21:02,075
(yue) 我冇辦法應承你
(en) I won't promise you


257
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:04,122
(yue) 佢會成為我嘅負累
(en) He'll be a burden to me


258
00:21:05,638 --> 00:21:09,123
(yue) 你都知見習魔法師
(en) You know that novice magicians


259
00:21:10,364 --> 00:21:12,059
(yue) 喺實戰嘅死亡率有幾高㗎啦
(en) have a high mortality rate in actual combat


260
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:13,931
(yue) 朋友交託個細路畀我
(en) A friend entrusted a child to me


261
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:13,931
(yue) 我唔打算送佢去死啊
(en) I don't plan to send him to his death


262
00:21:16,907 --> 00:21:17,990
(yue) 原來係噉
(en) I see


263
00:21:18,895 --> 00:21:20,990
(yue) 係噉，我想拜託你另一件事
(en) So, I have another favor to ask of you


264
00:21:26,448 --> 00:21:29,850
(yue) 呢本係由賢者埃維希個墓出土嘅文物
(en) This is an artifact from the tomb of the sage Evichi


265
00:21:30,645 --> 00:21:32,381
(yue) 聽講呢本魔道書
(en) I heard that this magic book


266
00:21:32,432 --> 00:21:34,938
(yue) 入面記載住而家已經失傳咗
(en) contains knowledge that has already been lost


267
00:21:34,962 --> 00:21:37,448
(yue) 可將死者復活嘅不死魔法
(en) about reviving the dead with undead magic


268
00:21:37,975 --> 00:21:41,049
(yue) 我唔覺得呢個世界上會有呢啲噉嘅魔法囖
(en) I don't think such magic exists in this world


269
00:21:41,488 --> 00:21:45,161
(yue) 所以我想你幫我手解讀呢個魔道書
(en) So I want you to help me decipher this magic book


270
00:21:45,543 --> 00:21:46,822
(yue) 可唔可以啊？
(en) Can you?


271
00:21:47,476 --> 00:21:49,662
(yue) 呢啲係用圖畫做嘅暗號？
(en) Is this a code using pictures?


272
00:21:49,713 --> 00:21:52,163
(yue) 呢個時代嘅人真係好鍾意呢啲嘢
(en) People of this era really like this kind of thing


273
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:55,380
(yue) 只要畀五六年我都得𠸏
(en) If you give me 5-6 years, I can do it


274
00:21:56,020 --> 00:21:57,191
(yue) 係噉樣呀？
(en) Is that so?


275
00:21:58,117 --> 00:22:01,019
(yue) 但係解讀呢啲嘢之後，你打算做咩啊？
(en) But after deciphering this, what do you plan to do?


276
00:22:01,043 --> 00:22:03,476
(yue) 你之前唔係話過你唔怕死㗎咩？
(en) Didn't you say you weren't afraid of death?


277
00:22:03,777 --> 00:22:05,843
(yue) 我噉做係有兩個理由
(en) I have two reasons for doing this


278
00:22:06,289 --> 00:22:10,523
(yue) 第一個係
(en) The first one is


279
00:22:07,504 --> 00:22:10,523
(yue) 我之前喺你哋面前噉講即係讕有型
(en) that I was just pretending to be cool in front of you guys


280
00:22:11,083 --> 00:22:15,120
(yue) 另一個理由係我比起之前變得更加怕死
(en) The other reason is that I've become more afraid of death than before


281
00:22:16,047 --> 00:22:18,445
(yue) 我唔使長生不死
(en) I don't need to be immortal


282
00:22:18,469 --> 00:22:19,720
(yue) 只想長命啲
(en) I just want to live a bit longer


283
00:22:20,422 --> 00:22:22,340
(yue) 長少少已經夠㗎喇
(en) A little longer is enough


284
00:22:22,391 --> 00:22:24,420
(yue) 我想要多啲啲時間
(en) I want more time


285
00:22:28,341 --> 00:22:30,201
(yue) 而且聖典都有寫啦
(en) And the scriptures say


286
00:22:30,252 --> 00:22:32,498
(yue) 人要健健康康噉生活
(en) that people should live healthy lives


287
00:22:32,576 --> 00:22:35,421
(yue) 長壽咪係最好嘅證明囖，芙莉蓮
(en) Longevity is the best proof, Frieren


288
00:22:35,798 --> 00:22:37,294
(yue) 你個酒肉和尚
(en) You, the wine and meat monk


289
00:22:39,681 --> 00:22:40,508
(yue) 啊，係喇
(en) Ah, yeah


290
00:22:40,967 --> 00:22:43,786
(yue) 喺你解讀嘅空檔時間都冇問題㗎
